{
  "stem": "20848.4",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And when I marched in at nighttime, I used to sell the peas for bread.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "The-- the-- the people, like the [GERMAN] and the kapos, they used to have plenty of bread.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they needed something nicer.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So that's how I used to sell it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And we had more than one portion of bread.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And it was a very bad camp, Majdanek.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They-- they were forever hanging people and beating people and they were-- I can't even tell you.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "For this-- without any reason at all, they would grab somebody and-- and-- and-- and beat them up, you know?",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we would-- were hanging two women, I don't know why.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And there was one very sadistic woman from Lithuania who used to go with a horse whip and used to whack-- you know, beat everybody up.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Anyway, one day, they made-- they said for everybody to congregate in the camp.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they said that they going to send transports away from Majdanek.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I think they must have been liquidating Majdanek.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And how shall I put it to you?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They took 2,000 women, and I had a-- made another selection.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I had a lot of trouble too-- that time too.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I was very lucky with the cigarettes, because there was again a doctor who was making the selection.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And my mother went through, and he started smoking a cigarette just as I was going to come through the selection.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And my mother grabbed me by the hand and pulled me towards her because they were again putting people to one side to death, and people to go to the transports.",
      "word_count": 31
    }
  ],
